des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your LookiLife products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our LookiLife app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our LookiLife app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search LookiLife skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable LookiLife skill, and you'll be navigated to LookiLife login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn on the plug.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, turn on the robot.”
“Alexa, show me the backyard camera.”
“Alexa, turn on the pet feeder.”
